# SS26-INITIAL-STOCK Allocation Verdict

## Executive Summary

The engine processed **3,536 styles** across **184 stores**, producing **649,152 allocation lines** and distributing **96,394 units** out of 210,907 received (**45.7% utilization**). The allocation completed successfully with no crashes, and **every store received stock** (0 stores were zeroed out).

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The allocation is **architecturally correct** but running in **cold-start mode** — all demand signals are coming from Tier 4/5 fallbacks because SS26 is a brand-new season with no direct SKU-level sales history. This is **expected behavior**, not a bug.

