## Confidence Distribution

| Confidence | Lines | Units | Avg Qty |
|---|---|---|---|
| HIGH | 16,512 (20%) | 7,473 | 1.48 |
| MEDIUM | 307,704 (47%) | 53,601 | 1.20 |
| LOW | 324,936 (33%) | 35,320 | 1.08 |

- **HIGH** = Style DNA matched with ≥20 weeks of analogous history
- **MEDIUM** = Style DNA matched with 5-19 weeks of history
- **LOW** = Minimum presentation fallback (no analogue found)

